He was - a blacksmith's striker. In them days when he was a young fellow. At Pool
ey's foundry at Kidsgrove. And - he worked his road up. In the engineering trade. From one firm to another. And - as years went on he eventually - went - blacksmithing then, from blacksmith's striker to the blacksmith.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15686718 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3684446\charrsid4418643 What would a blacksmith's striker do?
