Well a blacksmith's striker is the one as - slings the sledgehammer. See? And the blacksmith is the - the man as is doing the job. Which says - light, heavy, light heavy. He's - touching it with the hammer you see, and the striker's coming ove
r - with a sledgehammer, hitting his hammer, to hammer the - mat - the material out you see, the metal out. On the anvil that is you know.
