f - Quaker oats, and a cup of tea, you know, just - quick, get away. Of course this all happening while we - we're schooling - school days then wasn't it. And then - used to have sandwiches and - just snacks then 'til - 'til we have a - had a proper meal 
really when we come home - from school at night in the afternoon you see.
