 at Barley Green. He's - fire superintendant. To do with - petrol pumps and - fire extinguishers, seeing as all those are in - kept in proper working order. And - or if - ever there's a fire, he - has to go and - make enquiries, how it started and all tha
t. These - oil fires as you - hear about getting knocked over, setting the - place on fire and causing damage. All that he has to attend to.
