Cricket, football - used to have a - very comical game you - perhaps you wouldn't understand. We used to have a game of - five or six of us, 
standing - with a - agen the wall, and then one on top of the other, and - one had got to - kind of leap - and get on the first one, right over see, you know. And that was good exercise that was. To us. I - do what - I just forget what game we called that
. Yes. Yes. You stand behind - one behind the other - one'd - first one'd be his hands on the wall and the other behind him and so on, 'til he came out somewhere here. And then the ones as was jumping was - had got to clear the lot sort of style.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15686718 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3684446\charrsid4418643 Were 
